g/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Mike Cotton\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4062:\"\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-layout-26 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:33.3%\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-summary\">Summary</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"release-label has-normal-font-size\">Maintenance Release</p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:66.66%\">\n<p class=\"release-summary__overview has-medium-font-size\">The latest version of Event Tickets introduces several fixes and tweaks.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>As always, we recommend <a href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/knowledgebase/k/creating-and-using-a-wordpress-staging-site/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">testing updates</a> on a staging site first, but it should all be smooth sailing.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-layout-27 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:33.33%\">\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-fixed\"><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/2705.png\" alt=\"✅\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /> Fixed</h4>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:66.66%\">\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">Bugs that were squashed in this release:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Fixed updating stock data when Tickets Commerce attendees are moved.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Fixed showing duplicate order overview data from TribeCommerce when Event Tickets Plus is disabled.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Stock will be calculated correctly when an order fails and then succeeds while using Tickets Commerce.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Decode any HTML entities that appear in the subject line of outgoing emails.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Fixed multiple issues related to series pass check-ins.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Site Health will no longer fatal when providers are not setup.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-layout-28 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:33.33%\">\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-tweak\"><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/2728.png\" alt=\"✨\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /> Tweak</h4>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:66.66%\">\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">New tweaks in this release:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Use dynamic ticket labels within the block editor&#8217;s Tickets Block.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Added filters:<br><code>tec_tickets_move_attendees_ids</code><br><code>tec_tickets_attendee_manual_uncheckin_success_data</code><br><code>tec_tickets_attendee_uncheckin</code></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-layout-29 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:33.3%\">\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-translations\"><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f5e3.png\" alt=\"🗣\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /> Translations</h4>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:66.66%\">\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">Updated language files and strings:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>1 new string added</li>\n\n\n\n<li>56 updated</li>\n\n\n\n<li>2 fuzzied</li>\n\n\n\n<li>0 obsoleted</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/release-notes/event-tickets/event-tickets-5-8-3/\">Event Tickets 5.8.3</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com\">The Events Calendar</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:9;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Promoter 4.1.3\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:139:\"https://theeventscalendar.com/release-notes/promoter/promoter-4-1-3/?utm_source=theeventscalendar&utm_medium=referral&utm_campaign=rss-feed\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 06 Mar 2024 19:05:14 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8:\"Promoter\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"release notes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:40:\"https://theeventscalendar.com/?p=2543894\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:446:\"<p>Summary Maintenance and Feature Release Promoter 4.1.3 is a minor release that introduces enhancements and fixes for email queue management and improves error handling. ✨ Changed We made a few changes: ✅ Fixed We made a handful of fixes:</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com/release-notes/promoter/promoter-4-1-3/\">Promoter 4.1.3</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theeventscalendar.com\">The Events Calendar</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"Joel Liriano\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3072:\"\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-layout-30 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:33.3%\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-summary\">Summary</h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-normal-font-size\">Maintenance and Feature Release</p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:66.66%\">\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">Promoter 4.1.3 is a minor release that introduces enhancements and fixes for email queue management and improves error handling.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-css-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-layout-31 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:33.33%\">\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-changed\"><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/2728.png\" alt=\"✨\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /> Changed</h4>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:66.66%\">\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">We made a few changes:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Updated text and links in the footer. </li>\n\n\n\n<li>Send mail now happens with a failing strategy, which means the message will be sent again after a few minutes if the first attempt fails.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-css-opacity\"/>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-layout-32 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:33.33%\">\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\" id=\"h-fixed\"><img src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/2705.png\" alt=\"✅\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /> Fixed</h4>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:66.66%\">\n<p class=\"has-medium-font-size\">We made a handful of fixes:</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Enforcing From/Sender headers on all emails sent. Preventing problems with Caching in the queueing system.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Aligning template header image left/right will now show correctly.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>When creating a scheduled message, using On Event Start/End Date, the correct date will now be chosen.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Resolved error occurring with users that have no DNS entries set up.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Images are set to have an auto height in emails to avoid being vertically skewed.</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Resolved issues with messages not being sent due to unknown